{"tid":636313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Fandy Law：泛民請向梁天琦道歉　扮野並無意義","createTime":"2018-04-20T17:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T23:13:57.000Z","uid":47714,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"70120c752558624d2191ee04aec419836969a426","tid":636313,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:34:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=1884465221845634&amp;id=100008465224910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1884465221845634%26id%3D100008465224910&d=rmQRCwUQjDIqh2s8OWqFup4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f6898ea0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=1884465221845634&amp;id=100008465224910</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：Fandy Law<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/TBNrzg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FTBNrzg&h=b56ce119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆街泛民政棍，<br />\n為什麼不公開講，自己之前對本民前，對梁天琦的陰謀論是誤判？？？<br />\n講句說話難過去聽審？<br />\n大大聲道歉，謠言就收斂，好過去法庭聽審，這樣還像真的關心梁天琦，成班冚家剷，玩兩手，要光環時要光環，想絕人去路就抹黑，所以不道歉，卻敲鑼打鼓去聽審，仆街政棍！"},{"pid":"680886e12bb24af3c9551855d66e0a58a80a1194","tid":636313,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:41:59.000Z","msg":"true<br />\n不過港獨同本土派都係鬼，係中共派落黎搞事，想通過23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n補選近了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a825793ab476a165dd7ba0155557c51058ce9a","tid":636313,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T17:49:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"302c7c8cc98fcd2f683783ce23f60b83c5aae04b","tid":636313,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T19:11:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">@五毛狙擊手<br />\n@LIKLN<br />\n@食魚有魚味<br />\n@慕清流<br />\n@waiwaiwai<br />\n@求銀祈<br />\n@妙爾尼爾<br />\n@波台唔係台</span>"},{"pid":"188dfdb2b095b1